title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Week 5 in the NFL. Did the Tom Brady sack warrant a roughing the passer flag? Ross Tucker joins us for his weekly appearance and explains what makes the Ravens the 3rd best team in the AFC. And a caller catches Fritzy off guard. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
